root.title: Tokyo Shinjuu (Totempole)
root.author: Totempole
root.synopsis: From Bunny's Scanlations: Miyasaka decided to try his luck as assistant director in entertainment industry. His first impression of director Yano was not the best but it slowly started to changed after he managed to see his smile when they talked about a movie. It was originally released as a doujinshi and self published.
